{
  "stem": "3855.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was not a question of passing or denying, no matter how [INAUDIBLE] you wore lederhosen or not, which was a conventional dress in Austria.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't say that I felt, until the time of Hitler, that I felt this problem.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll be honest about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I will say that as soon as students became radicalized, they started to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this very friend whom I want to mention-- Ludwig [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Prater ?] was his name-- his brother was a strong Nazi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Ludwig used to warn me every time, stay home today, Karl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They're going to beat you guys up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I would.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I want to bring these things out to show the ambivalence in life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was in '37.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just prior.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Prior.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because engineering was not considered the Jewish trade in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the tradition was toward more different learnings-- medicine, law, accounting, as I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And engineers, really, it was also difficult to get a job for an engineer in Austria-- for a Jewish engineer, I will admit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was always my plan to go to Austria anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But once I graduated, things changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was anti-Semitism throughout industry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The engineering field is, or at least was-- also in this country, as I will later relate-- a Christian field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's only with the advent of electronics where the analytical mind, which is typical of Jews and also of certain Asians, came to the fore, rather than the space technology type of mind that is in machine construction, et cetera, that was needed before.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When that mind became more in demand, the field opened up for Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no more question about it--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in this country.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
